### ─── DASHBOARD TESTS ───────────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Login to get token (use your seeded student)
# @name loginStudent
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "universityEmail": "ali.hassan@ul.edu.lb",
  "universityId": "12345",
  "password": "yourpassword"
}

### Save token from login response (REST Client does this automatically with @name above)
@accessToken = {{loginStudent.response.body.accessToken}}

### 2. Dashboard — current calendar year (uses student's own calendarYear)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. Dashboard — filter to 2024
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard?calendarYear=2024
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Dashboard — filter to a year with no courses (expect empty list)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard?calendarYear=2020
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Dashboard — no token (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard

### 6. Dashboard — invalid token (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer invalidtoken123

